WEBVTT

00:00:00.996 --> 00:00:02.956
A few months ago,

00:00:02.996 --> 00:00:05.876
my daughter asked me
a very simple question:

00:00:05.916 --> 00:00:07.356
“Who are your heroes, dad?”

00:00:08.476 --> 00:00:11.116
I said, "Well, besides my father ..."

00:00:11.156 --> 00:00:12.796
hoping she would get the hint.

00:00:12.836 --> 00:00:14.476
(Laughter)

00:00:14.476 --> 00:00:17.716
